<br>
HP/AC base:  2109/632<br>
Crusty BP:     2186/661<br>
Crafted BP:    2160/666<br>
<br>
Crafted is 5 more AC, and 26hps less.  With the principle that 1 ac = 10hps is a good trade off, the crafted is the superior BP.  And if it does become an issue, choose the one you want, we all just toot our own horns anyway. =)<br>
<br>
Sorry to pick the detail here, but I'm up way past my bed time and it seems like a good idea.  Also, I wore a crafted BP with my crusty arms and legs, and I thought I was rather the seksi dorf on the town. <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=31658">Raun Stonecutter 55 Warrior</a>
